short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save and open groups of tabs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tired of cluttered browser windows with too many open tabs? With Tab Organizer, you can easily save your current tabs into named groups, organize them by task or project, and access them whenever you need.

Key Features:

1.Save all currently open tabs into a group with just one click.
2.Name your tab groups for easy identification.
3.Add or remove URLs from your groups anytime.
4.Reopen all tabs in a group instantly in a new window, keeping your work organized.
5.Perfect for managing multiple tasks, research, or projects, Tab Organizer simplifies your browsing experience. Save your tabs now and access them later with ease!
